Luminance / Radiance
========================================================

<img src = "https://www.gigahertz-optik.de/assets/Uploads/Abb.-II.11-neu-v03.png" />

***

* **Luminance** 
  + luminous intensity per unit area by an extended source
  + Units: candela/$m^2$, Foot-lamberts
* **Radiance**
  + radiant intensity per unit area by an extended source
  + Units: Watts/steridian/$m^2$
  
Measuring Luminance / Radiance
======================================================== 
...presenting a luminance meter:

<img src = "https://www.kemek.eu/en/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/2943363460_5b2bccbc_150-370x220.jpg" height="50%" width="50%" />


Illuminance / Irradiance
========================================================

<img src = "https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRSkBAl3sPe_EbN7pu9AWdwgJMxdNUCVRipVg&usqp=CAU" height="100%" width="100%" />

***

* **Illuminance** 
  + luminous intensity incident to a unit of surface area
  + Units: lux, lumens/$m^2$, Foot-candles
* **Irradiance**
  + radiant intensity incident to a unit of surface area
  + Units: Watts/$m^2$
  
